# geometricSeries

- _geometricSeries(count, start, multiplier)_

Answer a List holding a geometric series:

```
>>> 7.geometricSeries(1, 3)
[1 3 9 27 81 243 729]

>>> 7.geometricSeries(729, 1 / 3)
[729 243 81 27 9 3 1]
```

